  ],
  "description": [
    "Waits until the CANstress hardware is in the state Pending."
  ],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "Note With timeout = 0 an infinite time is waited until the state Pending occurs. Thus the additional test procedure is blocked if the state Pending is not reached.",
